@startuml
title Repository Structure - prometheus-grafana-demo

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam legendBackgroundColor #F5F5F5

legend left
  |= Icon |= Description |
  | <&folder> | Directory |
  | <&file> | File |
  | <&cog> | Configuration |
  | <&code> | Source code |
endlegend

salt
{
  {T
    + <&folder> **prometheus-grafana-demo**
    ++ <&cog> docker-compose.yaml | All 9 services orchestration
    ++ <&cog> prometheus.yml | Scrape targets for all services
    ++ <&file> .gitignore
    ++ <&file> README.md
    ++ <&folder> **services/**
    +++ <&folder> **order-service/** | REST API - order management
    ++++ <&code> app.py | FastAPI app with RabbitMQ publishing
    ++++ <&file> Dockerfile
    ++++ <&file> requirements.txt
    +++ <&folder> **inventory-service/** | REST API - stock levels
    ++++ <&code> app.py | FastAPI app with gauge metrics
    ++++ <&file> Dockerfile
    ++++ <&file> requirements.txt
    +++ <&folder> **payment-service/** | REST API - payment simulation
    ++++ <&code> app.py | FastAPI app with 15% failure rate
    ++++ <&file> Dockerfile
    ++++ <&file> requirements.txt
    +++ <&folder> **fulfillment-worker/** | Background job processor
    ++++ <&code> worker.py | RabbitMQ consumer, standalone metrics
    ++++ <&file> Dockerfile
    ++++ <&file> requirements.txt
    +++ <&folder> **load-generator/** | Auto traffic generation
    ++++ <&code> generator.py | Sends random requests to all APIs
    ++++ <&file> Dockerfile
    ++++ <&file> requirements.txt
    ++ <&folder> **web/** | React SPA frontend
    +++ <&code> Dockerfile | Multi-stage: node build + nginx
    +++ <&cog> nginx.conf | Reverse proxy to API services
    +++ <&file> package.json
    +++ <&folder> **public/**
    ++++ <&file> index.html
    +++ <&folder> **src/**
    ++++ <&code> index.js | App entry point
    ++++ <&code> App.js | Main layout with tab navigation
    ++++ <&code> Orders.js | Place orders, view history
    ++++ <&code> Inventory.js | Stock levels, restocking
    ++++ <&code> Payments.js | Payment simulator with burst mode
    ++++ <&code> Health.js | Service health dashboard
    ++ <&folder> **grafana/**
    +++ <&folder> **provisioning/**
    ++++ <&folder> **datasources/**
    +++++ <&cog> datasource.yml | Prometheus auto-configured
    ++++ <&folder> **dashboards/**
    +++++ <&cog> dashboards.yml | Dashboard provisioning config
    +++++ <&cog> ecommerce.json | Pre-built 8-panel dashboard
  }
}
@enduml
